if (noNote3) {
	if (noFeed) {
		feed fish
	}
}

remove note4
```

张三  | 李四
--- | ---
leave note3		| .
. 					| leave note4
.					| if (noNote3) {
if (noNote4) {	| .
remove note3	| .
. 					| remove note4
...					| ...
fish died			| .

##### 结论
- 不会被撑死了，可能会被饿死……
- 没解决问题

#### 方案 4

张三执行

```
leave note3

while (noNote4)
{
